metadata.name: Planet "Mycelium"
metadata.description:
MYCELIUM - An uncharted planet in the mouth of a Black Hole, acidic soil with salt crystals, wildling sapphire walkers in the trees, and poisonous slime mushrooms.
But this planet seems to be inhabited...

Fantasy is limitless, and I don't know what planets and experiments it will lead me to.
But this is only the beginning, I will drag you into my fantasy world )
